---
title: Chilled Tomato Gazpacho with Cumin Shrimp NOTE: Blender or Food Processor Required
description: This refreshing chilled vegetable soup brings together tomatoes, cucumbers, and scallions in a blender or food processor (required!) with a little bread and a dose of olive oil for rich, fruity smoothness. You’ll top the gazpacho with earthy cumin-spiced shrimp, and finish with a dollop of tangy yogurt and ciabatta toasts for crunchy contrast.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/664cb19f6aa70e05fa69017e-b509b261.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/664cb19f6aa70e05fa69017e-en-US.pdf
